description: Don't miss this terrific value proposition in prime South Boston location. 2 Bed/2 Bath corner unit comes equipped with a Chef's kitchen -- Quartz countertops, SubZero & Wolf Appliances. High ceilings and hardwood floors throughout. Pet friendly, A/C, In-Unit Laundry, and Sonos sound system. All of this in a full-service amenity building with concierge services and valet parking. Owners have full access to on-site Fitness Center, Dog Washing Station, Club Room, and Roof Deck. Just moments to the Broadway T-Stop (Red Line), I-93, Mass Pike, and award winning restaurants. Simple living awaits! Reach out today for access.
